Feed items usually arrive as **bare fragments** — no `<html>`, no `<body>`, just content.

They still deserve a faithful conversion, including [links with query strings](https://example.com/details?a=1&b=2) and images:

![a cat, obviously](https://example.com/cat.jpg)

1.  First point
2.  Second point with *emphasis*

And a line  
break.
